    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "main先有一个提交z，然后马上切出very-long-feature-branch。之后main继续开发，特性分支也持续提交，形成并行线。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit z",
        "very-long-feature-branch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把基础结构画出来：main分支起始，commit z，然后branch出very-long-feature-branch。接下来两边怎么交错？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "commit z",
        "very-long-feature-branch",
