      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到。所以特性分支总共三个提交f、g、h，main上有z、a、b，最后merge very-long-feature-branch。这个顺序我理解了，开始绘制。",
      "elements_involved": [
